  "title": "Medical Technologist/Sleep Technologist ( Full Time/ Part Time ) – Immediate #HVN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description: </strong></p><p>·        Assist doctors and healthcare providers to ensure smooth delivery of services </p><p>·        Check and calibrate equipment and instruments, ensure they are in good working condition </p><p>·        Perform Lung Function Tests, Sleep Monitoring Studies </p><p>·        Provide patients with instructions on follow up visits </p><p><strong>Requirements</strong>: </p><p>·        Diploma in Biomedical Science/Biotechnology </p><p>·        Preferably with 2 years of relevant experience in a clinical setting/hospital environment, with patient fronting experience </p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
